                           <desc>: Note concerning guarantors (?).</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The note is partly illegible due to faded ink. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The scribe used compressed script over erasure: <locus target="#117va">117va</locus>.
 - Tamallas-sign, in the shape of
                           two perpendicular lines (┴), indicating the place where the omissions,
                           written in the upper margin, belong: <locus target="#41ra">41ra</locus>,
                           116vb.
 - Tamallas-sign, in the shape of two perpendicular lines (├),
                           indicating the place where the omissions, written in the margin, belong:
                              <locus target="#7rb">7rb</locus> (right margin), 88ra (left
                           margin).
 - Omitted letters, words or lines inserted interlineally:
                           e.g., <locus target="#6vb">6vb</locus>, 46va, 58rb, 87vb, 120ra,
                           135rb.
 - Omitted letters or words added at the beginning of the line
                           in a secondary hand: e.g., <locus target="#5ra">5ra</locus>, 7va, 19va
                           (here in the main hand).
 - Erasures: e.g., <locus target="#6va">6va</locus>, 12ra, 42ra, 53vb, 67ra, 82va, 126ra.
 - Erasures
                           marked with thin black lines: e.g., <locus target="#6vb">6vb</locus>,
                           11vb, 40vb, 117va, 135va, 146ra.
 - Erasure marked with a frame in
