 - Corrections written
                           over erasures: e.g., <locus target="#5vb">5vb</locus>, 14ra, 48va, 67ra,
                           89ra, 147vb.
 - Immediate corrections indicated by encircling the
                           word or the passage in a black frame: e.g., <locus target="#47rb">47rb</locus>, 51rb, 80ra, 117rb, 133va.
 - Misplacement of a
